<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Controller_Request_Http::getHeader() is case sensitive for some HTTP headers although HTTP headers are case insensitive according to RFC 2616. Case sensitive headers include all those that are not in the $_SERVER superglobal variable such as "Content-Type" and "Content-Length".</p>

